<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238392>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 5. Speocera bioforestae sp. n. Male. 2 – 4. Female. 5. 2. Palp, retrolateral view. 3. Palp, prolateral view (arrow point to tibial enlargement). 4. Chelicerae, posterior view. 5. Internal genitalia, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238392/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238394>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 12. Speocera musgo sp. n. Male 9 – 10. Female 11 – 12. 9. Palp, retrolateral view. 10. Palp, prolateral view. 11. Internal genitalia, dorsal view. 12. Chelicerae, posterior view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238394/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238393>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 8. Speocera violacea sp. n. Male 6 – 8. 6. Habitus, dorsal view. 7. Palp, retrolateral view. 8. Palp, prolateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238393/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

